# Real-Time Live Tracking for D365 CRM with Azure Maps

## Overview

Build a mobile app (React Native / Expo) that authenticates users via Azure AD, tracks their GPS location in real-time with high accuracy, sends the data to Dynamics 365 CRM via Web API, and visualizes it in an Azure Maps web resource embedded inside CRM.

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A["📱 Expo Mobile App\n(Android/iOS)"] -->|"Azure AD Auth"| B["🔐 Azure AD\n(Entra ID)"]
    A -->|"GPS Location\n(every 5-10s)"| C["🌐 D365 Web API"]
    C -->|"CRUD"| D["📦 D365 CRM\nCustom Entities"]
    D -->|"Read"| E["🗺️ Azure Maps\nWeb Resource"]
    B -->|"Token"| C
```

---

